Sun Crusher:




Sun Crusher smiled at Baal's decision.  "You have made the correct choice.  
We will go back to a base of ours.  Though watch out for him," he said, 
pointing his launcher at Havoc, "no doubt he'll try and stop us.  So be on 
your guard."

The boosters in his feet began to power up.
